To set up the libraries and utilities:

cd $HOME/OpenFOAM/$USER-$OFVER
mkdir applications run
cd applications
clone //https://github.com/vitst/libsFoamAux

cd libsFoamAux
cp -p $HOME/OpenFOAM/install/mkInclude .
mkInclude
Allwmake

Note:
    Solvers and utilities are installed in parallel directories
